I'm sorry.

140
00:07:36,170 --> 00:07:37,460
Well...

141
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:40,410
Kaede called me over, saying there is something she wants to discuss.

142
00:07:40,410 --> 00:07:42,930
She's acting on her own again.

143
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:49,890
Hello, good afternoon.
